A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Primary and Secondary Education – Definition and Notification of Reportable
3 Offense – Alterations
4 FOR the purpose of altering the definition of “reportable offense” to remove the requirement
5 that the offense occurred off school premises and did not occur at an event sponsored
6 by the school; requiring the Department of Juvenile Services to report to the local
7 superintendent of schools and school principal for certain decisions made during a
8 certain inquiry of a juvenile offender for certain offenses; and generally relating to
9 reporting of arrests of students for reportable offenses.
10 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
